name: Studio Artist 5.5 by Synthetik - First Screenshot "In The Wild"
description: This is the first screenshot of Studio Artist 5.5 taken “in the wild,” signed by John Holland. Studio Artist mimics the human visual cortex, and uses learned techniques to create layers of representation and abstraction. Images are composed of layers of various procedures, including image processing, synthetic textures, modular synthesized graphics, and individual brushstrokes.
